        "风险有 owner 和下一步",
        "TaskResult 有质量评价",
        "通知链路有状态"
      ],
      "preEditRoleGate": [
        "workflow/task/risk/audit/handoff/status/acceptance-routing 属于 PM 可编辑范围",
